		</a>
	)}
	{youtube && (
		<a href={youtube} class="platform-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
			<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M23.498 6.186a2.99 2.99 0 0 0-2.104-2.117C19.505 3.5 12 3.5 12 3.5s-7.505 0-9.394.569A2.99 2.99 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.09 0 12 0 12s0 3.91.502 5.814a2.99 2.99 0 0 0 2.104 2.117C4.495 20.5 12 20.5 12 20.5s7.505 0 9.394-.569a2.99 2.99 0 0 0 2.104-2.117C24 15.91 24 12 24 12s0-3.91-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/></svg>
